NAME
    App::BlockWebFlooders - Block IP addresses of web flooders using
    iptables

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.010 of App::BlockWebFlooders (from
    Perl distribution App-BlockWebFlooders), released on 2019-01-29.

SYNOPSIS
    See the included block-web-flooders script.

